    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Daisaku Yokoyama</b>\n</p><p><b>Daisaku Yokoyama</b>,<br />\na Japanese computer scientist, <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">Shogi</a> programmer, and research associate at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Tokyo\">University of Tokyo</a> with interests in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parallel_computing\">parallel computing</a>, <a href=\"/Languages\" title=\"Languages\">programming languages</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robot_software\">robot programming</a>, <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">game-tree search</a>, and <a href=\"/Shogi\" title=\"Shogi\">computer-shogi</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. Daisaku Yokoyama is co-author of the Shogi engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gekisashi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gekisashi (page does not exist)\">Gekisashi</a>, Gold medal winner of the <a href=\"/15th_Computer_Olympiad#Shogi\" title=\"15th Computer Olympiad\">15th Computer Olympiad, Shogi</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanazawa,_Ishikawa\">Kanazawa</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daisaku_Yokoyama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daisaku_Yokoyama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka\" title=\"Yoshimasa Tsuruoka\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.2.9258\">Game-Tree Search Algorithm based on Realization Probability</a></i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka\" title=\"Yoshimasa Tsuruoka\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Maruyama\" title=\"Takashi Maruyama\">Takashi Maruyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/article/200218/000020021802A0583583.php\">Implementation of \"Gekisashi\". A Computer Shogi Player</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sciencelinks.jp/j-east/journal/J/L0461A/2006.php\">Joho Shori Gakkai Natsu no Puroguramingu, Shinpojiumu Hokokushu</a>, <a href=\"/Makoto_Miwa\" title=\"Makoto Miwa\">Makoto Miwa</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/6180u7h3t312468u/\">Automatic Construction of Static Evaluation Functions for Computer Game Players</a></i>. ALT ’06 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Makoto_Miwa\" title=\"Makoto Miwa\">Makoto Miwa</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2007</b>). <i>Automatic Generation of Evaluation Features for Computer Game Players</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cswww.essex.ac.uk/cig/2007/papers/2037.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daisaku_Yokoyama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Akira_Ura\" title=\"Akira Ura\">Akira Ura</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takashi_Chikayama\" title=\"Takashi Chikayama\">Takashi Chikayama</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/ipsjjip/21/1/21_17/_article\">Two-level Task Scheduling for Parallel Game Tree Search Based on Necessity</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/jip/jip21.html#UraYC13\">Journal of Information Processing, Vol. 21, No. 1</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kunihito_Hoki\" title=\"Kunihito Hoki\">Kunihito Hoki</a>, <a href=\"/Tomoyuki_Kaneko\" title=\"Tomoyuki Kaneko\">Tomoyuki Kaneko</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daisaku Yokoyama</a>, <a href=\"/Takuya_Obata\" title=\"Takuya Obata\">Takuya Obata</a>, <a href=\"/Hiroshi_Yamashita\" title=\"Hiroshi Yamashita\">Hiroshi Yamashita</a>, <a href=\"/Yoshimasa_Tsuruoka\" title=\"Yoshimasa Tsuruoka\">Yoshimasa Tsuruoka</a>, <a href=\"/Takeshi_Ito\" title=\"Takeshi Ito\">Takeshi Ito</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/6598505/\">A System-Design Outline of the Distributed-Shogi-System Akara 2010</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/snpd/snpd2013.html\">SNPD 2013</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daisaku_Yokoyama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=717\">Daisaku Yokoyama's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://jp.linkedin.com/pub/daisaku-yokoyama/8/886/525\">Daisaku Yokoyama - Japan</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LinkedIn\">LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daisaku_Yokoyama&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://jp.linkedin.com/pub/daisaku-yokoyama/8/886/525\">Daisaku Yokoyama - Japan</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LinkedIn\">LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#RefDB\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Reference Database</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/David_Levy\" title=\"David Levy\">David Levy</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilk.uvt.nl/icga/journal/contents/content25-3.htm#SOME%20COMMENTS%20ON%20REALIZATION%20PROBABILITIES\">SOME COMMENTS ON REALIZATION PROBABILITIES AND THE SEX ALGORITHM</a></i>.<a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#25_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 25, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www-alg.ist.hokudai.ac.jp/~thomas/ALT06/progfin.pdf\">The 17th International Conference on Algorithmic Learning Theory</a> (pdf)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228160849\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocess